response.original_title: GCW vs Renegades of Wrestling Australian Tour 2023, August 25th
response.overview: On August 25th starts the GCW's Australian Tour 2023 and the first stop is the Roundhouse in Kensington, NSW. The event features the Gringo Loco vs El Hijo del Vikingo match.  Also in the lineup:  Charli Evans vs Maki Itoh  Three Way Match Robbie Eagles vs Lochy Hendricks vs Everett Connors  ROW Women's Title Three Way Match Aysha (c) vs Steph De Lander vs Lena Kross  Tag Team Match BUSSY (Allie Katch & Effy) vs PPK (Frankie B & Nikki Van Blair)  Tag Team Match Back Pain (Backman & Jack Pain) vs Bastard Brothers (Gore & KrackerJak)  ROW Title Match Caveman Ugg (c) vs Joey Janela
response.title: GCW vs Renegades of Wrestling Australian Tour 2023, August 25th
